        "=(-i)(1+i)+(1+i)2.\n",
        "$$\n",
        "So\n",
        "$$\n",
        "(-i)(1+i)=-i-i^2=1-i,\n",
        "$$\n",
        "and\n",
        "$$\n",
        "2(1+i)=2+2i.\n",
        "$$\n",
        "Thus\n",
        "$$\n",
        "\\langle u,v\\rangle=3+i.\n",
        "$$\n",
        "By conjugate symmetry,\n",
        "$$\n",
        "\\langle v,u\\rangle=3-i.\n",
        "$$\n",
        "Finally,\n",
